B.OI=new A.U(B.ae,"\u2708\ufe0f Exam Tip","Common exam confusion pairs:\n\u2022 **IAS** (Indicated Airspeed) vs. **TAS** (True Airspeed) \u2014 TAS increases with altitude\n\u2022 **FMS** manages the whole route | **autopilot** controls the aircraft\n\u2022 **TCAS RA** = mandatory evasive action | **TCAS TA** = Traffic Advisory (awareness only)\n\u2022 **DME** measures **slant range** (not ground distance)\n\u2022 **IRS** is self-contained (no external signals) | **GPS** needs satellites",null,null,null)
