B.a2B=new A.aa(-301,B.b7,461,'"Contrary to standard operating procedures" means:',B.WO,1,B.A,null,null,null)
B.WH=s(["The main cause was crew rest","Crew rest was one element that made the accident more likely","Crew rest alone caused the accident","The crew rested adequately"],t.s)
B.a2w=new A.aa(-302,B.b7,462,'"A contributing factor was the inadequate crew rest period." This means:',B.WH,1,B.A,null,null,null)
B.To=s(["It is confirmed that","There was not enough evidence to establish","It is unlikely that","The investigation did not examine"],t.s)
B.a2g=new A.aa(-303,B.b7,463,'"It could not be determined whether\u2026" in a report means:',B.To,1,B.b_,null,null,null)
