B.Pf=new A.U(B.ac,"Advanced completion requires full context understanding","At the advanced level, sentence completion questions involve complex technical sentences where multiple options may seem grammatically correct. The correct answer requires understanding both grammar **and** aviation technical knowledge.",null,null,null)
B.OM=new A.U(B.B,"\u2699\ufe0f Technical Collocation Patterns",'Aviation technical writing has fixed collocations \u2014 word combinations that are always used together:\n\n\u2022 perform/carry out/conduct (**a maintenance check**) \u2014 not "make" or "do"\n\u2022 comply with (**regulations**) \u2014 not "follow to"\n\u2022 in accordance with (**AMM/CMM**) \u2014 standard phrase\n\u2022 prior to/following (**departure**) \u2014 formal time expressions\n\u2022 serviceability of (**equipment**) \u2014 airworthiness term\n\u2022 within the limits (**specified in**) \u2014 compliance language',null,null,null)
B.On=new A.U(B.B,"\ud83d\udcd0 Precision Language","Aviation English values **precision** over elegance. Words are not interchangeable:\n\u2022 **inspect** = visually examine | **test** = functionally verify | **check** = confirm state\n\u2022 **fault** = specific defect | **failure** = complete loss of function | **malfunction** = partial/intermittent failure\n\u2022 **serviceable** = fit for use | **unserviceable** = not fit for use (technical term, not informal)\n\u2022 **advise** = inform/recommend | **instruct** = give mandatory direction",null,null,null)
B.KW=new A.aE("All repairs must be carried out __________ the Aircraft Maintenance Manual.","T\xfcm onar\u0131mlar U\xe7ak Bak\u0131m El Kitab\u0131na uygun olarak yap\u0131lmal\u0131d\u0131r.","in accordance with")
B.KR=new A.aE("The component was declared __________ after a detailed visual inspection.","Par\xe7a, ayr\u0131nt\u0131l\u0131 g\xf6rsel incelemenin ard\u0131ndan kullan\u0131lamaz ilan edildi.","unserviceable")
